[h1]This plugin is a part of upcoming "Endless Sky: Captain's Edition" reboot of the base game. Stay tuned - meanwhile, installing the plugins can help to preview the experience, together or in parts.[/h1]

Undisruptive Animated Stars for Endless Sky. Updated to work with latest ES (0.9.10+) and maintained to be compatible in future.


[h1]Features[/h1]

[list][*]Every star system was hand-tweaked for the star to match lore/star type of vanilla Endless Sky.
 
[*]Full integration with dynamic fuel/solar energy gathering.


[h1]Installing[/h1]

Check:
https://github.com/Cat-Lady/animated-stars-nova/releases

...for latest, pre-packaged version.


[b]1.[/b] Unpack [i]animated-stars-nova[/i] to your ES plugins folder. Be sure that you have single [i]animated-stars-nova[/i] directory inside your plugins folder, containing [i]data[/i] and [i]images[/i] folders. Directory structure should look like:

[code](...)/plugins/animated-stars-nova/(.../data/, /images/ and other stuff)[/code]

It [b]won't[/b] work if the directory structure will be anything like:

[code](...)/plugins/animated-stars-nova/animated-stars-nova/(...)[/code]


